Text: Your dayPST Cooper So tell me how was you squash game Good I hope I have been so busy lately but I did get a game in yesterday but late and I had to go to the police gym with a friend cause I could not get a time at the Y but tonight I am playing there and have a court already so that really works for me Well I hope you are well and still able to meet up sometime Take care Corinna Johnston Client Relationship Officer Tel Fax Email

REPST Well I am in but not in I am going to Kelowna tonight and tomorrow but will be in town Sunday to Tuesday but I will be out again till Friday I know I am in next weekend From there on I am not too sure what is happening but let me know if any of that works for you How was your holidays How are things at work or are you working right now I heard a lot of people go laid off and others are still not steady I see your address is still Enron Well let me know Always Corinna Original Message From mailto Sent Friday January AM To Subject RE Hey i just got back into town from almost weeks vacation sorry i didnt get in touch over the holidays but do you want to get together sometime soon my schedule is very easygoing at them moment hopefully you are in town cooper Original Message From Johnston Corinna Corinna ntriacomENRON Sent Thursday December PM To Richey Cooper Subject Hello and how are you Are you going away for the Christmas Holidays Let me know maybe we will get together for some egg nog sometime Corinna Johnston Client Relationship Officer Tel Fax Email This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you

One more try to mail youPST Bottom line I do like you I enjoy the time we spend together but I do not get a good feeling from you I do not get any vibe from you and that bothers me I am not looking for someone to spend the night with and then not talk to after I need more than that I really do For me being intimate is not just a passing thing I do not like how things have been since the night I stayed at your place and I really thought that you would have wanted to be around a little more Cooper I am not trying to make your decisions for you and I am not trying to put words in your mouth and I apologize if it came across that way during our conversation I want more than what we have right now and I am sorry if I made you believe otherwise I wanted to see you tonight because it has been a long time since last we were together but I am not going to play second fiddle You knew we had plans you have known for more than a week and you could have declined your drink invitation or rescheduled for another time I am not the type of person who likes to be squeezed into a schedule it does not work for me You can either write back to this email or give me a call sometime after till then I will be in meetings Corinna Johnston Client Relationship Officer Tel Fax Email

Good MorningPST Cooper I was wondering if you would want to do lunch today we could meet up in the middle if you would like After all we both need to eat Let me know soon Corinna Johnston Client Relationship Officer Tel Fax Email
